msgid "Check this option if you want to use Google reCAPTCHA on the booking/cancel/membership forms, to thwart spammers a bit. Currently only supports reCAPTCHA v2 Tickbox. You can then either add #_CAPTCHA to your form layout yourself or it will automatically added just above the submit button if not present."
